name: JellyCar 2
description:
JellyCar 2 comes fully loaded with more than 30 levels ranging from easy to hard and tilt! Includes Classic, Long Jump and Factory modes! Post high scores, best times, and longest jumps in the Hall of Fame. You can even create and play custom levels! With so much squishy goodness, you’ll want to drive JellyCar 2 all around town!
